What you need to know:

Bayern have won the Bundesliga eight years running, although Dortmund have finished runners-up five times in that period, including in the last two campaigns.Bayern have also won 10 of their last 14 Bundesliga meetings since winning their 2013 Champions League final showdown. They also triumphed 3-2 when the sides clashed in the German Super Cup recently.This time, though, the teams are level atop the Bundesliga and Dortmund are in fine form, with Erling Braut Haaland on 10 goals for the season.